6// RenderTargetMtl.mm:
7// Implements the class methods for RenderTargetMtl.
8//
9
10#include "libANGLE/renderer/metal/RenderTargetMtl.h"
11
12namespace rx
13{
14RenderTargetMtl::RenderTargetMtl() :
15 mTextureRenderTargetInfo(std::make_shared<mtl::RenderPassAttachmentTextureTargetDesc>()),
16 mFormat(nullptr)
17{}
18
19RenderTargetMtl::~RenderTargetMtl()
20{
21 reset();
22}
23
24RenderTargetMtl::RenderTargetMtl(RenderTargetMtl &&other)
25 : mTextureRenderTargetInfo(std::move(other.mTextureRenderTargetInfo))
26{}
27
28void RenderTargetMtl::set(const mtl::TextureRef &texture,
29 const mtl::MipmapNativeLevel &level,
30 uint32_t layer,
31 const mtl::Format &format)
32{
33 setWithImplicitMSTexture(texture, nullptr, level, layer, format);
34}
35
36void RenderTargetMtl::setWithImplicitMSTexture(const mtl::TextureRef &texture,
37 const mtl::TextureRef &implicitMSTexture,
38 const mtl::MipmapNativeLevel &level,
39 uint32_t layer,
40 const mtl::Format &format)
41{
42 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->texture = texture;
43 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->implicitMSTexture = implicitMSTexture;
44 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->level = level;
45 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->sliceOrDepth = layer;
46 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->blendable = format.getCaps().blendable;
47 mFormat = &format;
48}
49
50void RenderTargetMtl::setTexture(const mtl::TextureRef &texture)
51{
52 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->texture = texture;
53}
54
55void RenderTargetMtl::setImplicitMSTexture(const mtl::TextureRef &implicitMSTexture)
56{
57 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->implicitMSTexture = implicitMSTexture;
58}
59
60void RenderTargetMtl::duplicateFrom(const RenderTargetMtl &src)
61{
62 setWithImplicitMSTexture(src.getTexture(), src.getImplicitMSTexture(), src.getLevelIndex(),
63 src.getLayerIndex(), *src.getFormat());
64}
65
66void RenderTargetMtl::reset()
67{
68 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->texture.reset();
69 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->implicitMSTexture.reset();
70 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->level = mtl::kZeroNativeMipLevel;
71 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->sliceOrDepth = 0;
72 mTextureRenderTargetInfo->blendable = false;
73 mFormat = nullptr;
74}
75
76uint32_t RenderTargetMtl::getRenderSamples() const
77{
78 return mTextureRenderTargetInfo->getRenderSamples();
79}
80void RenderTargetMtl::toRenderPassAttachmentDesc(mtl::RenderPassAttachmentDesc *rpaDescOut) const
81{
82 rpaDescOut->renderTarget = mTextureRenderTargetInfo;
83}
84}
